### 🎨 Branding

This folder contains additional CSS tweaks that build on top of the **Ultrachromic** theme by CTalvio.

> ⚠️ **You need to apply the Ultrachromic base theme first before using these tweaks!**

**How to apply the base theme:**
1. Go to your Jellyfin **Admin Dashboard** in your web browser
2. Navigate to **Dashboard → General → Branding**
3. Paste the following code into the **Custom CSS** field:
```css
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/presets/kaleidochromic_preset.css');
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/header/header_transparent.css');
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/login/login_minimalistic.css');
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/progress/floating.css');
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/effects/glassy.css');
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/episodelist/episodes_compactlist.css');
@import url("https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/intro-skipper/intro-skipper-css@main/skip-button.min.css");

:root { --skip-hide-duration: 8s; }

.emby-tab-button::before { font-size: 28px; margin-right: 10px; }

.emby-tab-button.tab-home::before        { content: "home";           font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-favorites::before   { content: "favorite";       font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-watchlist::before   { content: "bookmark";       font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-bookmarkadd::before {
    content: "bookmark_add";
    font-family: 'Material Symbols Rounded';
    font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

.emby-tab-button.tab-filme::before       { content: "movie";          font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-vorschlaege::before { content: "lightbulb";      font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-favoriten::before   { content: "favorite";       font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-sammlungen::before  { content: "folder_copy";    font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-genres::before      { content: "theater_comedy"; font-family: 'Material Icons'; }

.emby-tab-button.tab-serien::before      { content: "tv";             font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-demnaechst::before  { content: "event";          font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-folgen::before      { content: "playlist_play";  font-family: 'Material Icons'; }

.emby-tab-button.tab-musik::before       { content: "music_note";     font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-alben::before       { content: "album";          font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-kuenstler::before   { content: "mic";            font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-playlisten::before  { content: "queue_music";    font-family: 'Material Icons'; }

.emby-tab-button.tab-fotos::before       { content: "photo_library";  font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-buecher::before     { content: "menu_book";      font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-personen::before    { content: "group";          font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
.emby-tab-button.tab-studios::before     { content: "domain";         font-family: 'Material Icons'; }
